SXOpeningElement","jsx-a11y/anchor-is-valid","The href attribute requires a valid value to be accessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value. If you cannot provide a valid href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/HEAD/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","react/jsx-no-target-blank","Using target=\"_blank\" without rel=\"noreferrer\" (which implies rel=\"noopener\") is a security risk in older browsers: see https://mathiasbynens.github.io/rel-noopener/#recommendations","noTargetBlankWithoutNoreferrer",{"range":"131","text":"132"},[1092,1092]," rel=\"noreferrer\""]